title: Cyberpunk 2077 no tendrá un sistema de moralidad
body:
#Cyberpunk2077 no tendrá un sistema de moralidad

Según ha confirmado CD Projekt Red, en Cyberpunk 2077 no hay lugar para las decisiones binarias; dependerá de los jugadores el no matar a nadie durante el juego.

Cyberpunk 2077 no contará con un sistema de moralidad en sí mismo. La ciudad de Night City, escenario donde se desarrolla la acción del juego, no tiene sitio para aquellas decisiones tipo “blanco o negro”, y así lo ha confirmado CD…

summary: I can’t wait to meet meaningful characters in Cyberpunk 2077. Remembering how CDPR treated the Witcher 3 in terms of npcs really...
body:
I can’t wait to meet meaningful characters in Cyberpunk 2077. Remembering how CDPR treated the Witcher 3 in terms of npcs really makes me feel at ease. Who will steal our hearts? Who will be our friend during tough times? Who will betray us and become our enemy? Most importantly; can we fuck our enemies into a rivalry relationship? Asking important questions here. 

Honestly though, I’m most excited to develop another virtual family that will impact us. (Think Witcher 3 anniversary video). For those who have little to no family in the waking world, it would be breathtaking to feel like you belong somewhere. Even if it’s in Night City. Can’t wait to be there..

summary: Glavni fokus u Cyberpunk 2077 je na ponovnom igranju i slobodi igrača
title: Glavni fokus u Cyberpunk 2077 je na ponovnom igranju i slobodi igrača
body:
Glavni fokus u Cyberpunk 2077 je na ponovnom igranju i slobodi igrača

Od objave datuma izlaska, za Cyberpunk 2077 vlada izuzetno veliko interesovanje i veliki broj igrača se interesuje za aktivnosti koje ih očekuju u tom futurističkom svetu, kao i koliko će vremena provesti u igri.

Već je objavljeno da će Cyberpunk 2077 imati više završetaka, a uz to će imati i 2-3 velike ekspanzije, a sada smo od glavnog dizajnera igre, Pavel Sasko, saznali još detalja o ovom…
